Detailed Description

cvmx_led_udd_dat#

LED_UDD_DAT = User defined data (header or trailer)

Notes: Bits come out LSB to MSB on the shift chain. If LED_UDD_CNT is set to 4 then the bits comes out LED_UDD_DAT[0], LED_UDD_DAT[1], LED_UDD_DAT[2], LED_UDD_DAT[3].
